    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/22621c4468004e29acc8b44d4fb2a10a.avif?t=1770780658\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/c823691df9fce5696e02c1bb67af91fe.poster.avif?t=1770780658\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/c823691df9fce5696e02c1bb67af91fe.webm?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/c823691df9fce5696e02c1bb67af91fe.mp4?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in complex first person turn based combat against a <strong>variety of dangerous enemies</strong>. <strong>Sequence</strong> your skills and learn each enemy’s strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/081b8460a14d4e332b830dfeea1e7299.avif?t=1770780658\" width=800 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/f075b292c30cf6418631991636b76947.poster.avif?t=1770780658\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/f075b292c30cf6418631991636b76947.webm?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/f075b292c30cf6418631991636b76947.mp4?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create <strong>strategic builds</strong> by selecting Tethers to wield, slotting them into your inventory, and forming a network of powerful <strong>Gear Modifiers</strong> to ensure victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/717217a6eb1fe0c182dde2eb3d7ca267.avif?t=1770780658\" width=800 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/74d92c4ae6b43bcaa2e9a315ba0e141e.poster.avif?t=1770780658\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/74d92c4ae6b43bcaa2e9a315ba0e141e.webm?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/74d92c4ae6b43bcaa2e9a315ba0e141e.mp4?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enhance and <strong>Upgrade</strong> your gear at the Blacksmith. Every <strong>Tether</strong> weapon has a unique passive that changes your gameplay, and you may <strong>Modify</strong> your weapons to suit your strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/62fc3213454cc9e3773170e82a893be7.avif?t=1770780658\" width=800 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/260e61dc1aaab5b1bf720933e84e13c7.poster.avif?t=1770780658\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/260e61dc1aaab5b1bf720933e84e13c7.webm?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/260e61dc1aaab5b1bf720933e84e13c7.mp4?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore perilous dungeons and abandoned cities filled with useful gear and constant danger in an <strong>isometric third person perspective</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/ba06b4bda8e5a000194b41a7c5a7196d.avif?t=1770780658\" width=800 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/da68d2401090d29a673b09ba971e2b93.poster.avif?t=1770780658\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/da68d2401090d29a673b09ba971e2b93.webm?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116170/extras/da68d2401090d29a673b09ba971e2b93.mp4?t=1770780658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Encounter characters at the caravan hub, or out in the wild. Utilize them for their services while <strong>learning about their past and future</strong>, and in turn, discover the <strong>dark history of the Lords</strong> and their impact on the lands.</p>",
